Public Sub teNotes_Change()
   
   If bExit Then Return
   '-------------------------------------------------------------
   'DO NOT be smart and make me Last (ie don't use Last.whatever)
   'this change event is called external to this form
   'see FInboxDocumentPage.Editor_Init()
